import React, { useEffect, useState } from 'react' const BlogAdd = () => { const[formData, setFormData] = useState({ title:'', content:'', category:'', file:null, }) const[user, setUser] = useState({}) useEffect(()=>{ const ls = localStorage.getItem('user') setUser(JSON.parse(ls)) },[]) const[uploading, setUploading] = useState(false) const handleChange=(e)=>{ const{name, value} = e.target.value setFormData((prevData) => ({ ...prevData, [name]: value, })); } console.log(user) return(

Hi {user.username}

This information will be displayed publicly so be careful what you share.

Write your blog content here.

or drag and drop

PNG, JPG, GIF up to 10MB

) } export default BlogAdd {/*
*/}
